ActCanadian High Arctic Research Station Act
PrecisReappointment of LISEANNE FORAND of North Saanich, British Columbia, as Vice-Chairperson of the Board of Directors of the Canadian High Arctic Research Station, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year or until such time as a new Vice-Chairperson is appointed, whichever occurs first, effective June 21, 2022.
